{"tid":2008324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛年花16億出差費　陳馮富珍住總統套房　每晚逾千美元","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T03:54:38.000Z","uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4f49c97c2f11e431022e82ef919ef26d63489238","tid":2008324,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"而家吹雞話冇錢？"},{"pid":"2328a2a6772a40a67276e275d07683971298d02d","tid":2008324,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"根據美聯社取得的世界衛生組織（WHO）內部文件，世衛組織人員每年的出差費高達約2億美元（約15.6億港元），總幹事陳馮富珍更遭質疑作風奢華，花大錢搭頭等艙和住總統套房。<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織正舉行大會，將選出新一任總幹事，接替下月離任的陳馮富珍。被拒出席大會的台灣，其官方媒體中央社，今天有大篇幅報道美聯社揭發世衛出差費高昂的消息。報道指，隸屬聯合國的世衛組織以經費拮据為由，呼籲各界踴躍捐輸，以利處理全世界衛生危機，但卻未能控制自家的出差經費。儘管聯合國採行新的規定，想要節制昂貴的出差費，高級官員在內部抱怨，員工仍違反規定訂購商務艙的機票以及五星級飯店的房間。"},{"pid":"952c2509fbfacda5800ea509a850293f9114bd9b","tid":2008324,"uid":249866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"9664d9afd5d337816f151608918580d68911b7fb","tid":2008324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"80920cf1d076ddb8fa10dbee6905c6799042ce60","tid":2008324,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9664d9afd5d337816f151608918580d68911b7fb","tid":2008324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"Why so early"},{"pid":"e35c73999668292d2010bbac6b5ebdfdd50fdc3c","tid":2008324,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"冚家鏟雞珍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00a05ca9719ada0cb999e0e697c4e23eab39643","tid":2008324,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\